data.description: Two-story ; 4 bedrooms ; 3.5 baths ; study ; game room ; covered patio ; two-car garage. The large upstairs game room overlooks a two-story family room and gallery over foyer. Downstairs study with glass french doors is adjacent to the kitchen. The modern kitchen features stainless appliances, bright cabinets, white quartz countertops, a single bowl stainless steel sink, brushed nickel hardware, and pendant lights. Main Suite includes an oversized shower. The covered patio comes with gas line for outdoor cooking. The staircase combines classic iron spindles with wood detail. Wood-like tile in main areas blends with nuetral carpet and paint. Security system is pre-wired. Yard is fully sodded and includes landscaping in front and full sprinkler system.Home is available for immedaite move-in Chesmar Homes is the builder!
